Being able to speak more languages, especially those related to emerging economies, will give children better opportunities to find good jobs.
In Scotland if each school teaches in different languages.
Many schools will focus on the more classical modern languages, while others will teach in the languages considered most valuable to the UK on the way to 2020, such as Mandarin and Japanese.
